rows.label: kizunainn066_msg0001
rows.name:
Sorry to bother you, everyone, but
there's somewhere I'd like to visit.

rows.label: kizunainn066_msg0003
rows.name:
I was hoping to take a look at the
Stele of Judgment in Spirit Crucible
Elpys. Would you take me there?

rows.label: kizunainn066_msg0004
rows.name:
I mean, sure, I guess...
But are you sure? That place is
pretty tough on Blades.

rows.label: kizunainn066_msg0005
rows.name: I'm always up for a challenge!
